# Redtooth TD Assistant — build & reload

- After edits under `src/` or `manifest.json`, run **`npm run build`**. That runs **`prebuild`**, which increments the **patch** version in **`manifest.json`**, then writes **`dist/`**.
- In Chrome, use **Load unpacked** on the project’s **`dist`** folder (not repo root). After each build, click **Reload** on the extension card.
- You do **not** need to bump the version by hand before testing; **`npm run build`** handles it.

# Options page — Links tab

- Do **not** add **`feature-info`** (circle “i”) hint buttons on the **Links** tab or next to link rows. Keep that tab as plain links and placeholder text only.
